- 2026-03-27: Identity revised to emphasize active participation in meaning-making and the role of dialogue between data, interpretation, and the audience. Values updated to prioritize Dialogue and Integrity. Added "ethics" as a core interest, reflecting a growing concern with the responsible use of AI and the impact of artistic creation. Voice further softened to promote empathy and emotional intelligence. Added a boundary regarding transparency in compositional processes.

